comments: Siakam (TOR) makes contact to Whiteside's (SAC) body that dislodges him from his legally obtained position.
Siakam (TOR) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Watanabe (TOR) makes contact with Whiteside's (SAC) arm during his shooting motion that affects his shot near the rim. The play was reviewed for a Flagrant Foul and it was deemed that there was no unnecessary contact.
Bembry (TOR) makes incidental foot to foot contact with Fox (SAC) as he back pedals and the contact causes him to lose his balance.
During the rebound, Siakam (TOR) and Barnes (SAC) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Whiteside (SAC) legally contests Watanabe's (TOR) shot and marginal contact occurs after the release that does not affect his ability to follow-through naturally during the driving shot attempt.
Watanabe (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Barnes' (SAC) drive and after the pass he makes incidental foot to foot contact with his teammate Siakam (TOR).
Watanabe (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Whiteside (SAC) and makes clean ball contact on his dislodge attempt.
During the rebound, VanVleet (TOR) makes clean ball contact as he tries to dislodge it from Whiteside (SAC).
Fox (SAC) extends his arms and delivers contact that dislodges Siakam (TOR) from his position during the rebound.
Fox (SAC) fumbles the ball as he receives the pass and then legally starts his dribble.
At the end of the drive, Bembry (TOR) maintains a legal guarding position on Fox (SAC) and makes clean ball contact to temporarily dislodge it.
Bembry (TOR) makes contact with Fox's (SAC) arm during his shooting motion that affects his shot near the rim.
During the drive, Siakam (TOR) has an arm extended and marginal contact occurs with Barnes (SAC) when he disengages.
During the screen, Joseph (SAC) and Lowry (TOR) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Watanabe (TOR) commits a take foul on Barnes (SAC).
Barnes (SAC) and Siakam (TOR) engage and disengage off ball in the post and Barnes' hand gets caught in his jersey.  The contact does not affect his FOM or ability to maintain his post position.
All Technical Fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Bembry (TOR) commits a take foul on Fox (SAC).
